# ZMODEM wire-capture fixtures and their payload inputs are binary —
# they contain raw protocol bytes with specific line endings that must
# survive a Windows checkout unchanged.  Without this, git's autocrlf
# normalizes LF → CRLF inside the payload files, and the Windows CI job
# fails the `test_lrzsz_replay_*` and `test_upload_save_integration_*`
# tests with a CRLF-in-left / LF-in-right assertion mismatch.
tests/fixtures/*.bin       binary
tests/fixtures/*.payload   binary
